EN: The accident caused him to be disabled.

ZH: 他因为这次手术而致残。
EN: He was disabled due to this surgery.

ZH: 小女孩因为疾病致残了。
EN: The little girl was disabled by the illness.

ZH: 这种罕见疾病会致残患者。
EN: This rare disease will disable the patient.

ZH: 他的摔跤事故导致他致残。
EN: His wrestling accident left him disabled.

ZH: 一场悲惨的事故致残了整个家庭。
EN: A tragic accident disabled the entire family.

ZH: 失去了一条腿致残了他。
EN: Losing a leg disabled him.

ZH: 我们需要提供帮助给那些致残的人。
EN: We need to provide assistance to those who are disabled.

ZH: 我们应该为致残者提供更多支持。
EN: We should offer more support to the disabled.

